<title>Deriving the a‚ÄìR relation ‚Äî FCC ¬∑ BCC ¬∑ HCP</title>
<style>
  :root{--navy:#1F3864;--steel:#2E5496;--terra:#B85042;--teal:#1F7A63;--amber:#E8890C;
    --ink:#21262E;--mut:#6B7480;--line:#C7CFDA;--bg:#F1F4F8;--gold:#F2B705;}
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html,body{margin:0;height:100%;font-family:Calibri,"Segoe UI",system-ui,sans-serif;color:var(--ink);background:var(--bg);}
